# ğŸ¢ Turtle Race Game

A fun and beginner-friendly Turtle Graphics project made using Python's built-in **turtle** module.
Multiple turtles race across the screen, and the player predicts which turtle will win!

---

## ğŸ® Features

* Colorful turtles with different speeds
* Randomized movement
* User betting/prediction
* Simple and fun gameplay
* Beginner-friendly code using the turtle module

